@startuml
title Frontend CI/CD (As-Is)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho

actor Dev
participant "GitHub Repo" as Repo
participant "GitHub Actions\nfreshfood-ci-cd" as GHA
participant "frontend-ci\n(Node 20)" as FCI
participant "build-and-publish-images" as CD
database "GHCR" as GHCR

Dev -> Repo: Push / Open PR
Repo -> GHA: Trigger workflow\n(path includes test1/frontend/**)
GHA -> FCI: Checkout\nnpm ci\nnpm run build
FCI --> GHA: pass/fail

alt Event = push AND frontend-ci pass\n(and backend-ci pass)
  GHA -> CD: Build frontend image
  CD -> GHCR: Push freshfood-frontend:<sha>
else pull_request
  GHA -> GHA: Skip image push
end

note right of CD
As-is:
- Build stage dung Docker + nginx
- Chua co deploy step frontend\n(staging/prod)
end note

@enduml
